HEADWORD: Niveous
<hw>Niv"e*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>niveus</ets>, fr. <ets>nix</ets>, <ets>nivis</ets>, snow.]</ety>
<def>Snowy; resembling snow; partaking of the qualities of snow.</def>
